data.title: Warriors #34 Mike Dunleavy Jr. Autographed Rookie 8x10 Color Action Photo
data.meta_description: This 8x10 color action photo of Mike Dunleavy Jr. is a must-have for any Golden State Warriors fan. The photo captures Dunleavy Jr.'s rookie season with the team, making it a unique addition to any basketball memorabilia collection. The photo is signed by Dunleavy Jr., adding to its value and making it a great gift for any fan of his. This particular photo is from a regular season or playoff game, adding to its historical significance. Don't miss out on the opportunity to own this rare piece of basketball history.
